<br>
Q 2. If you can somehow keep his songs dispelled long enough to nuke him to death, yea. However, I suggest *not* picking fights with bards. <br>
<br>
If you don't kill them in the first round of song dispelling then they'll prolly just Selo's off and heal song to full. Try getting an air or earth pet with sow, resist magic, and the highest haste spell you can find. If you have the backstabbing water pet then use it instead. Hope the pet can keep the bard bashed/stunned/interrupted long enough for you to nuke to death. Only an idea tho. =/<br>
